44
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:57,760
<i>Muchas cosas confundían a Mary.</i>

45
00:05:57,760 --> 00:06:01,958
<i>Especialmente su madre,
Vera Lorraine Dinkle.</i>

46
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:06,960
<i>Para Mary, Vera siempre 
parecìa temblorosa.</i>

47
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:09,793
<i>Una linda pelota.
