48
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:13,868
<i>A Vera le gustaba escuchar el
cricket mientras horneaba.</i>

49
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:17,920
<i>Y su ingrediente principal
siempre era el jerez.</i>

50
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:21,000
<i>3/44. Y Thompson 2/15...</i>

51
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,880
